oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 10th Anniversary Pittie Festival in Nashville
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: festivals; Split Fountain Printing; anniversaries;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and split fountain, red to yellow on white) announcing the 10th Anniversary Pittie Festival 2017 at Centennial Park on October 22. Poster features a metal photoplate of a Pitbull cartoon designed by Lee Copeland.
